snippet.title: I made an idle gardening game (release devlog)
snippet.description:
Ruben introduces the 95th Patreon game: Tuin!

You can claim a key here if you were a Sokpop Patron in July: https://sokpop.co/patreon_access/

Support us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/sokpop

Check it out on Itch.io : https://sokpop.itch.io/tuin

Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/invite/Ye3HrWW
